ntskit-info-box-title\">\n                    Professionalism                <\/h3>\n                        \t\t  <p>As part of his training, he learned various things like language, combat skills, and culture, and was deployed throughout the country with the Special Operations Command<\/p>\n                                <\/div>\n        \n        \n                <\/div>\n                <\/a>\n        <\/div>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2ffa7cf e-con-full e-flex lakit-col-width-auto-no e-container e-con e-child\" data-id=\"2ffa7cf\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e2c576a ekit-equal-height-disable elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-icon-box\" data-id=\"e2c576a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" >        <!-- link opening -->\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"ekit_global_links\">\n                <!-- end link opening -->\n\n        <div class=\"elementskit-infobox text-center text- icon-top-align elementor-animation-  gradient-active  hover_from_bottom\">\n                    <div class=\"elementskit-box-header elementor-animation-\">\n                <div class=\"elementskit-info-box-icon  \">\n                    <i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"elementkit-infobox-icon icon icon-badge\"><\/i>\n                <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"box-body\">\n                            <h3 class=\"elementskit-info-box-title\">\n                    Approach                <\/h3>\n                        \t\t  <p>Hudson shares details about the missions he went on and the pictures supporting these missions throughout the year in Afghanistan.<\/p>\n                                <\/div>\n        \n        \n                <\/div>\n                <\/a>\n    